<?php

namespace Database\Seeders;

use Illuminate\Database\Seeder;
use App\Models\Resume;
use App\Models\Experience;
use App\Models\Education;
use App\Models\Skill;
use App\Models\Certification;

class ResumeSeeder extends Seeder
{
    public function run()
    {
        $resume = Resume::create([
            'name' => 'Jauie Canon',
            'address' => 'Taal, Pulilan, Bulacan | Pulilan, Philippines, 3005',
            'phone' => '09495689082',
            'email' => 'jauiecanon@gmail.com'
        ]);

        $resume->experiences()->createMany([
            [
                'title' => 'Logistics Assistant',
                'company' => 'Orovet Farm',
                'location' => 'Paltao, Pulilan',
                'start_date' => '2024-07-01',
                'end_date' => '2024-09-01',
                'description' => 'Coordinated efficient movement of goods, improving delivery timelines by 20%.'
            ],
            // Add more experiences as needed
        ]);

        $resume->education()->createMany([
            ['degree' => 'Bachelor of Science in Information Technology', 'institution' => 'Baliwag Polytechnic College', 'start_date' => '2021-01-01', 'end_date' => '2025-01-01'],
            // Add more education records as needed
        ]);

        $resume->skills()->createMany([
            ['skill_name' => 'Logistics & Supply Chain Management'],
            // Add more skills as needed
        ]);

        $resume->certifications()->createMany([
            ['title' => 'Full Course in Inventive Media', 'organization' => 'Inventive Media', 'date_obtained' => '2024-01-01'],
            // Add more certifications as needed
        ]);
    }
}
